{"type":"message","id":"a6cb1aa7","parentId":"d0cf3159","timestamp":"2026-04-14T09:49:24.178Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_fWvFCMby6WKJKLfUtcktKKDW|fc_0802d21a63301ba70169de0da0869081938de35c7fd074ca9c","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# USER.md - About Your Human\n\n_Learn about the person you're helping. Update this as you go._\n\n- **Name:**\n- **What to call them:**\n- **Pronouns:** _(optional)_\n- **Timezone:**\n- **Notes:**\n\n## Context\n\n_(What do they care about? What projects are they working on? What annoys them? What makes them laugh? Build this over time.)_\n\n---\n\nThe more you know, the better you can help. But remember — you're learning about a person, not building a dossier. Respect the difference.\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1776160164175}}
